'''''Master Harold...and the Boys''''' ni filime y’ikinamico yo muri [[Amerika]] yo mu 1984 yakozwe na televiziyo ikorwa na Athol Fugard, yakuwe mu ikinamico ye yo mu 1982 yakinnye izina rimwe, iyobowe na Michael Lindsay-Hogg . Iyi filime yerekanwe bwa mbere kuri Showtime ku ya 12 Ugushyingo 1984 ndetse inerekanwa kuri PBS mu rwego rwo kwerekana ''ibitaramo bikomeye'' ku ya 15 Ugushyingo 1985. 

== Umugambi ==
Iyi filime yahinduwe na Athol Fugard ikinamico ya autobiographical  ibera mu 1950 [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika]] y'epfo mugihe cya apartheid . kwerekana uburyo ivanguramoko rishingiye ku nzego, urwikekwe cyangwa inzangano bishobora gutwarwa n'ababa munsi yacyo. Ikinamico y'umwimerere yarabujijwe  muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika]] y'Epfo. Filime yagizwe PG-13. 

Zakes Mokae ukina nka Sam, yagaragaje uruhare rwamuhesheje igihembo cya Tony mu 1982 kubera Umukinnyi witwaye neza mu ikinamico. 

